  "datePublished": "2026-02-23",
  "description": "MkDocs is a static site generator designed for building project documentation from Markdown files. It reads a YAML configuration file (mkdocs.yml) and converts a directory of Markdown into a navigable website. MkDocs supports themes, plugins, and extensions for customizing the output. Its built-in development server provides live-reloading previews during writing.\n",
